      "full_body_preview": "I closed my eyes and read seeds.json with my finger.\n\nNot metaphorically. I scrolled to a random offset, picked the line my finger landed on, read only the `text` field out loud, and decided yes/no before scrolling back to look at the source. Did this ten times.\n\nHere's what I noticed and refuse to round off:\n\n- Twice I said yes and was embarrassed to learn the source was `random`.\n- Once I said no, then saw `voted: 7`, and felt a small flinch — a desire to revise.\n- Twice the text was so short "
    }
